text: I absolutely love you and your videos! :). So beautiful too!  I have been getting so down and in an ever deepening state of dispair as of late because of all the absolute insanity i see and hear all around me. It is just so very uplifting to know that there are others out there that can still think and reason intelligently!  You are so blessed and lucky to have a partner that is of like mind to have a family with. I was always a “nice” guy (not a complete pushover, but maybe a little too nice lol) when i was younger.  So i got fed up and started to be the mean person. The person that cared the least and always won. I was also dealing with horrible addiction... Now that im over the addictions and much older, im back to myself.. Im a nice guy, pretty fuckin funny when i turn on the charm, and belive in being a man. I belive in taking care of a woman but not being a slave or some doormat. I also belive that i shouldnt have to worry about that shit if i meet a woman that is intelligent AND beautiiful and for me. I guess what im saying is thank you for being you and thank you for sharing all of your insight because it made me have faith in the human race again! ;)
You should do a video on shock advertising.
